This will be decisive for the distribution of losses between the financial sector and the government," Marek said this week, for the iHNed.cz server.
Whether the plan is approved now or at the beginning of next week is not, according to Marek, so relevant.
"Much more important is that, as early as this week, congressmen agree on their support and give their approval as soon as possible.
